.com/a/Vdv5JgB</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AnonymousMockingjay]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>In Germany, a boy who loved motorcycles was diagnosed with a terminal illness. His family posted online asking if riders could come to cheer him up. They expect 20-30 people, but 15,000 motorcyclists showed up.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Z8YS0ci</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/T2bfine.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Saying hello, goodbye.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Z8YS0ci</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TerribleBot]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>My wife of 25 years died and her memorial service is tomorrow</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/MKlrQsh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7g93zrd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I thought I would scream into the void a bit as a treat. My wife died a few days after her 53rd birthday and her memorial is tomorrow.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cTJrXoS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I miss her horribly. My son is kind of a wreck emotionally. I've had to do everything on a shoestring budget because of course funeral expenses are f**king outrageous.
A big shout out to Jim's Funeral Home in Hurst, TX for one having of the few affordable options for cremation. I have recommended it to all my friends. (I also recommend them for everyone I hate but for entirely different reasons) Cece's family has a family plot at the Grove Hill cemetery, but since its owned by Dignity™, the price to do anything there is stupidly high.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8nZzJNc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>She suffered from a huge number of medical problems, and honestly I should have seen it coming because she had gotten so much weaker over the last couple of months. But it still caught me by surprise.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tiOkr3Y.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I thought we would grow old together, looked forward to it. Anyway, thanks for taking the time to read this. I just needed to talk about her.

EDIT: Thank you all so much for your kind words, I appreciate everything. If you are in the Dallas area and don't have anything better to do tomorrow you are all welcome to attend her memorial service.  
It will be at the Mesquite Church of Christ (400 W Davis St, Mesquite, TX 75149) at 10/18/2025 at 1pm. She grew up in the Church of Christ and it was the most appropriate option for a memorial. Say what you will about the Church of Christ in general, but the ladies of the church really f**king know their desserts.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/MKlrQsh</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Anarchduke]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>One of these guys</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/x90NfCN</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8VVrfVL.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Posted by Gavin Newsom</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/x90NfCN</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[slimvictor]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>It takes two to cure a hangover</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Mzdct2N</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/w95M1Od.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Mzdct2N</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[BillYouMurrayMe]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>War and Peas in Therapy (and Ljubljana)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/QHUDrYN</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GXuY9ov.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2EFCthb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VwKlTkx.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9ws1vsL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7K0VPEQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>We just got back from Tinta Stripa Festival in Slovenia and we had so 